---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Advertising Disclosure | CareCost Intelligence"
  description="Review the current non-monetized status of CareCost Intelligence and the disclosure rules that will apply if advertising or affiliate partnerships are introduced later."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Advertising Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="note">Updated: Mar 2026. Ads, sponsored placements, and affiliate monetization are not currently active on this site.</p>
      <div class="tag">Last updated: Mar 2026</div>
      <div class="editorial-meta">Reviewed by CareCost Intelligence Editorial Team</div>
      <div class="author-box">
        <div class="author-title">Disclosure review</div>
        <div class="author-meta">
          <div>
            <strong>CareCost Intelligence Editorial Team</strong>
            <p class="note">This page explains the site's current non-monetized status and the guardrails that will apply if monetization is introduced later. Read our <a href="/editorial-policy/">Editorial Policy</a> or <a href="/contact/">report a correction</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="chip-grid" style="margin-top: 12px;">
        <a class="chip" href="#current-status">Current status</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#future-ads">Future advertising</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#future-affiliate">Future affiliate links</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#labeling">Disclosure rules</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#tracking">Future data and tracking</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#independence">Editorial independence</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="current-status">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Current status</h2>
      <p>Ads, sponsored placements, and affiliate monetization are not currently active on this site.</p>
      <p class="note">If advertising or affiliate relationships are introduced later, this page will be updated before those changes go live.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="future-ads">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Future advertising guardrails</h2>
      <p>If advertising is added in the future, it will be limited to clearly designated placements and will not control our cost modeling or planning guidance.</p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>Sponsored placements would be labeled and visually separated.</li>
        <li>Editorial content would remain independent of advertising sales.</li>
        <li>Paid placements would stay out of estimator outputs, checklists, and quote workflows.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="future-affiliate">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Future affiliate link rules</h2>
      <p>If affiliate links are introduced later, they will be disclosed clearly before users are asked to rely on them.</p>
      <p class="note">We would not share personal care details or browser-local estimator inputs with affiliates as part of that change.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="labeling">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Disclosure and labeling rules</h2>
      <p>Any future monetization would be labeled clearly so users can distinguish sponsored material from editorial planning guidance.</p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>Sponsored placements would be easy to identify.</li>
        <li>Editorial pages would keep separate review standards.</li>
        <li>Any monetized relationship would be reflected in the relevant policy pages.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="tracking">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Future data and tracking disclosures</h2>
      <p>No advertising or affiliate tracking stack is currently active on this site.</p>
      <p class="note">If future monetization introduces cookies, pixels, analytics, or ad measurement tools, those changes will be disclosed in both this page and the privacy policy before launch.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="independence">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Editorial independence</h2>
      <p>Our content is created to support planning accuracy and user outcomes. Sponsorship does not and will not determine recommendations, rankings, or the tools we publish.</p>
      <p class="note">See our <a href="/editorial-policy/">Editorial Policy</a> for more detail.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="contact">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this disclosure can be sent to <a href="mailto:hello@carecostintel.com">hello@carecostintel.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
